# Coverage Exclusions
#
# Files and patterns excluded from code coverage analysis.
# These exclusions follow industry best practices for Go projects.

# CLI entry points (main packages)
# Justification: main() functions are not testable via unit tests
# Business logic is tested separately in *_test.go files
cmd/*/main.go

# Generated code
# Justification: Generated files should not be counted in coverage metrics
**/mock_*.go
**/*_gen.go
**/wire_gen.go

# Third-party code
# Justification: External dependencies are not our responsibility
vendor/**

# Documentation examples
# Justification: Example code is not production code
examples/**
